show.description: Andy catches her fiancé red-handed with another woman. Enraged, she calls off the wedding immediately—and in a shocking twist, marries a doctor she’s just met. What she doesn’t realize is… that same doctor has secretly loved her for the past three years. Now, with a broken past and an unexpected husband, what turn will Andy’s life take?
